<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti samadhigata pañcama
<lb n="2" break="no"/>hāśabda <hi rend="bold">pallavānvaya</hi> śrī prithuvīvallabha
<lb n="3"/><hi rend="bold">noḻambadi Arasa<unclear>n</unclear></hi> prithuvīrājyaṁgeye
<lb n="4"/><hi rend="bold">prithuvīpati</hi> Arasannāḍāḷe Ēḍeyū
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ra toṟugoṇdu parivalli mūlagu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ndurarmmagankāḍakuṭṭi Antiṟidu
<lb n="7"/>bīḻdan Avaṁge kalnāḍu koṭṭommāra
<lb n="8" break="no"/>siṁgarasammamma<unclear>ga</unclear> nmāramayya nko<note n="4-1">The letterga is engraved faintly.</note>
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṭṭadu Okkaṇḍuga kaḻani Idansa
<lb n="10" break="no"/>lisidōnaśvamētadā phalame
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ydugu<unclear>ṁ</unclear> Idana Aḻivōnvāraṇaśi
<lb n="12"/>yan Aḻida pañcamahāpātakan <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied>
</p>

